# Internal / dev files that must NOT be deployed or crawled.
# These are design references, build tooling, and working docs — not public
# pages. Serving them created stale, duplicate content (e.g. an old copy of the
# homepage with outdated path/lesson counts and pricing) that leaked to search
# engines and AI assistants. Excluding them here makes those URLs 404 so they
# deindex.

